You got your results back yet?


119
00:07:50,800 --> 00:07:52,160
Nope.


120
00:07:55,040 --> 00:07:57,000
HE GROANS


121
00:07:57,000 --> 00:07:58,280
What's bugging you?


122
00:07:58,280 --> 00:08:00,160
Had a phone call this morning.


123
00:08:03,200 --> 00:08:04,880
They want me to go to Washington


124
00:08:04,880 --> 00:08:09,280
