157
00:09:56,800 --> 00:09:58,080
Taxi!


158
00:10:06,600 --> 00:10:07,640
It's cold.


159
00:10:08,680 --> 00:10:10,200
NASA headquarters.


160
00:10:10,200 --> 00:10:12,480
NASA, you got it.


161
00:10:12,480 --> 00:10:13,520
Cold!


162
00:10:17,440 --> 00:10:19,000
