406
00:23:59,120 --> 00:24:00,560
Chairman Rogers...


407
00:24:01,520 --> 00:24:04,320
The boats just pulled in
the crew compartment.


408
00:24:07,280 --> 00:24:10,720
Can you tell me,
was the oxygen activated?


409
00:24:13,600 --> 00:24:15,120
Yes, Dr Ride.


410
00:24:15,120 --> 00:24:16,600
It was.


411
00:24:17,600 --> 00:24:18,960
We...


412
00:24:18,960 --> 00:24:21,840
maybe won't make that public
straight away.


413
00:24:22,960 --> 00:24:24,400
Excuse me.


414
00:24:40,760 --> 00:24:42,120
Dr Feynman.


415
00:24:43,200 --> 00:24:48,240
It's very important that this team
stays together all the time.


416
00:24:48,240 --> 00:24:49,400
Why?


417
00:24:50,760 --> 00:24:53,960
It's been reported to me that
you spent some time at Marshall.


418
00:24:53,960 --> 00:24:55,800
Alone.


419
00:24:55,800 --> 00:24:57,360
That's not very helpful.


420
00:24:57,360 --> 00:25:00,880
Oh, Mr Rogers, I don't find it
helpful to stand around.


421
00:25:01,880 --> 00:25:05,360
The other commissioners
are just being respectful.


422
00:25:05,360 --> 00:25:07,760
And you're saying I'm not?


423
00:25:09,720 --> 00:25:13,680
You understand the implications
of the oxygen being activated?


424
00:25:13,680 --> 00:25:15,160
I do.


425
00:25:15,160 --> 00:25:17,560
The astronauts
had to do that themselves.


426
00:25:18,800 --> 00:25:20,640
