00:29:15,080 --> 00:29:17,200
That's what we call the diamond.


495
00:29:17,200 --> 00:29:20,080
Wow, now that is very beautiful.


496
00:29:24,560 --> 00:29:26,560
RATTLING


497
00:29:26,560 --> 00:29:28,800
What the hell?


498
00:29:28,800 --> 00:29:31,160
You happy with that,
with that vibration?


